narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely! But only if you're interested in film-making, since making a movie is extraordinarily time intensive. But so worth it.
its the best class-Take it if you can!!

You need to take this class if you want to learn how to make a short film. You are required to take this if you want to take advanced fiction film. You should take if you want to explore filmmaking in-depth for a semester and really be challenged to write, direct and film.
